1
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:15,939
What's so special about that slut?

2
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:19,300
Gu Qisen and Gu Chengyan are both after her.

3
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:21,500
If Ji Xiaoxue and Gu Chengyan team up,

4
00:00:22,180 --> 00:00:23,700
I'm afraid I won't stand a chance.

5
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:27,980
You must keep a firm hold on Xia Wanqing.

6
00:00:28,739 --> 00:00:29,859
The Xia family behind her

7
00:00:29,859 --> 00:00:31,220
is our only support.

8
00:00:32,739 --> 00:00:33,700
I see, mom.

9
00:00:46,580 --> 00:00:47,499
Gu Chengyan,

10
00:00:48,739 --> 00:00:50,540
now between me and Ji Xiaoxue,

11
00:00:50,819 --> 00:00:51,940
you can only choose me.

12
00:00:53,900 --> 00:00:55,819
You've already chosen Gu Chengjing.

13
00:00:57,459 --> 00:00:58,859
We're in a marriage alliance.

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:01,379
Business is about mutual need,

15
00:01:02,180 --> 00:01:04,100
but marriage is a personal choice.

16
00:01:04,939 --> 00:01:06,980
The Gu family has two sons,

17
00:01:07,219 --> 00:01:09,779
but the Xia family only has me.

18
00:01:10,219 --> 00:01:11,700
You think you're choosing,

19
00:01:12,139 --> 00:01:13,659
but you're actually being chosen.

20
00:01:14,180 --> 00:01:16,299
And this wife might just be a title.

21
00:01:17,219 --> 00:01:19,779
So your marriage isn't a choice,

22
00:01:20,419 --> 00:01:21,219
but a necessity.

23
00:01:22,900 --> 00:01:23,700
Gu Chengyan,

24
00:01:24,540 --> 00:01:25,859
if you don't choose me,

25
00:01:26,260 --> 00:01:27,460
won't you regret it?

26
00:01:28,859 --> 00:01:29,900
That's how life is.

27
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:31,779
Sometimes you have no choice.

28
00:01:32,019 --> 00:01:33,019
If you have no choice,

29
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:35,139
then why regret?

30
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:38,859
Since there's no choice,

31
00:01:42,019 --> 00:01:43,460
might as well choose to accept

32
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:45,740
or even enjoy it.

33
00:01:47,659 --> 00:01:48,540
Isn't this

34
00:01:49,659 --> 00:01:51,139
a choice?

35
00:02:24,100 --> 00:02:24,859
Wanqing,

36
00:02:25,739 --> 00:02:26,459
marry me.

37
00:02:30,619 --> 00:02:32,940
My brother married you for profit

38
00:02:33,739 --> 00:02:35,139
and to become the heir.

39
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,179
But I'm different.

40
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:40,299
I really love you.

41
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:46,260
Are you willing to give up your shares?

42
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:49,339
I'm not afraid.

43
00:02:51,060 --> 00:02:51,859
Are you?

44
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:54,780
Gu Chengyan has hurt my heart

45
00:02:55,060 --> 00:02:56,419
and my self-esteem.

46
00:02:59,380 --> 00:03:00,139
Would you?

47
00:03:02,419 --> 00:03:03,700
I would never.

48
00:03:16,980 --> 00:03:18,299
Come on, have a drink.

49
00:03:18,579 --> 00:03:19,260
Okay.

50
00:03:54,220 --> 00:03:55,419
I knew you were here.

51
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,859
Let's talk.

52
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:02,179
I've been wanting to talk to you for a long time,

53
00:04:03,139 --> 00:04:04,899
but I don't know what to talk to you about.

54
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:08,700
We are like a play.

55
00:04:10,100 --> 00:04:12,339
But I don't want it to be a tragedy,

56
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,139
nor do I want the Gu family to be a tragedy.

57
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:17,579
If I hadn't met you

58
00:04:18,339 --> 00:04:19,740
or fallen in love with you,

59
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:20,820
maybe...

60
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:21,779
I love you too.

61
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:24,899
I will continue to love you in the future.

62
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:26,860
It's just that our identities are different.

63
00:04:27,979 --> 00:04:29,820
It's something we can't change.

64
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:31,820
I never thought

65
00:04:31,820 --> 00:04:33,380
to be the third daughter of the Gu family,

66
00:04:33,579 --> 00:04:35,539
or I don't want to be.

67
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:36,860
But I did.

68
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:40,860
Because I want to give you all the shares

69
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:41,579
Mr. Gu gave me.

70
00:04:44,979 --> 00:04:45,579
No.

71
00:04:46,139 --> 00:04:47,099
I can't take it.

72
00:04:48,899 --> 00:04:51,339
I can be in the company because of you.

73
00:04:51,820 --> 00:04:53,139
I only trust you.

74
00:04:54,579 --> 00:04:56,740
I won't give the shares to Gu Chengjing.

75
00:04:57,339 --> 00:04:59,139
Don't let us all down.

76
00:05:00,099 --> 00:05:00,779
Okay?

77
00:05:07,620 --> 00:05:08,899
Maybe this is fate.

78
00:05:13,099 --> 00:05:14,940
When we were in this room before,

79
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:18,139
you weren't my sister yet.

80
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:23,779
You hit the target.

81
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:39,139
I haven't learned archery yet.

82
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:43,019
Can you teach me later?

83
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:44,459
Brother.

84
00:06:14,940 --> 00:06:15,740
You first.

85
00:06:18,420 --> 00:06:19,019
Brother.

86
00:06:19,459 --> 00:06:20,339
Do you want candy?

87
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:23,060
Sure.

88
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:33,820
Chengyan, do you want one?

89
00:06:37,139 --> 00:06:37,940
No, thanks.

90
00:06:51,099 --> 00:06:51,740
Come in.

91
00:06:57,219 --> 00:06:58,740
Chengyan, are you looking for me?

92
00:06:59,579 --> 00:07:00,740
Don't call me Chengyan.

93
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:02,500
Tell me,

94
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:05,060
why did you give shares to Gu Chengyan?

95
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,979
Because I want him to be the heir of the company.

96
00:07:10,579 --> 00:07:11,899
What do you think

97
00:07:12,219 --> 00:07:13,860
will happen

98
00:07:14,979 --> 00:07:16,820
if he finds out

99
00:07:18,099 --> 00:07:19,139
about our relationship?

100
00:07:23,060 --> 00:07:23,940
Don't forget,

101
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,060
you have to do what I say.

102
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:35,420
Yeah,

103
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:39,659
what would he do to you

104
00:07:42,019 --> 00:07:43,579
if he found out about our relationship?

105
00:07:47,019 --> 00:07:47,740
No,

106
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:51,899
what would he do to you

107
00:07:52,019 --> 00:07:53,139
knows about your relationship,

108
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,620
what would he do to you?

109
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:00,620
No, no, no.

110
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:03,579
If what you did

111
00:08:04,219 --> 00:08:05,219
was known by Mr. Gu

112
00:08:05,339 --> 00:08:07,620
and everyone in the company,

113
00:08:10,659 --> 00:08:11,979
what would happen to you?

114
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:18,019
So,

115
00:08:18,779 --> 00:08:20,860
it's not that I need to listen to you,

116
00:08:23,019 --> 00:08:24,979
but you need to listen to me.

117
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:35,739
Be good.
